  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个极简的状态转换图，核心就是两个状态：State1和State2，它们之间有一条直接的连线。标题就叫\"Very simple diagram\"吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "State1",
        "State2",
        "title"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，双向箭头还是单向？另外无障碍阅读这块需要加accTitle和accDescr吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "State1",
        "State2",
        "accTitle",
        "accDescr"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "用单向箭头就够了，从State1指向State2。无障碍信息加上吧，accTitle写\"This is the accessible title\"，accDescr写\"This is an accessible description\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "State1",
        "State2",
        "accTitle",
        "accDescr"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把基础结构搭出来：两个状态节点、单向连线、标题和无障碍描述都加上了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "State1",
        "State2",
        "title",
        "accTitle",
        "accDescr"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，箭头方向我好像说反了需求——不对，单向是对的，但让我再确认下：State1到State2，没错。不过连线类型用实线还是虚线有区别吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "State1",
        "State2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "当前用的是默认实线（--）。如果需要强调状态迁移的某种特性，可以换虚线或加标注，但极简风格的话实线最干净。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "State1",
        "State2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "保持实线，就这样。accDescr的冒号后面好像需要空格？你检查一下格式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "accDescr"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "发现了，accDescr冒号后缺空格，已修正为\"accDescr: This is an accessible description\"。现在所有元素都就绪了。",
